title: Familiar faces ready to star (again) in Big 12 this season
text:
> Texas Familiar faces ready to star (again) in Big 12 this season Kayla McLain, a videographer for Texas Christian University, uses a chair to get on the same level as TCU basektball players Chris Washburn, left and Karviar Shepherd during NCAA college basketball Big 12 conference media day in Kansas City, Mo., Tuesday, Oct. 20, 2015.
